text: Michelle Heimberg (born 2 June 2000) is a Swiss diver. She competed in the women's 1 metre springboard event at the 2019 World Aquatics Championships. She finished in 16th place in the preliminary round. In the women's 3 metre springboard event she finished in 28th place in the preliminary round. ==References== Category:2000 births Category:Living people Category:Swiss female divers Category:Place of birth missing (living people) Category:Divers at the 2018 Summer Youth Olympics
